» Maintenance Assistant | IKEA | Al Ain – Al Futtaim Group – Dubai Jobs
Posted on 02 May 2014. Tags: , , , , , ,
About the Business:
One of the companies bearing Al-Futtaim name is IKEA.
IKEA is the world’s largest home furnishings store,
founded in Sweden over 60 years ago. At IKEA not only our furniture is down to earth,
straightforward and inspiring,
but so is our work ethics. Despite being the leading home furnishing retail franchisee across the world,
we at IKEA still give you the room to grow! At IKEA "creating a better everyday life for the many" isn’t only our vision,
it’s our way of life!
About the Job:
* Assists in providing an integrated HS&M operational 24 hours / day,
365 days / year within IKEA store.* Assists ensuring provision of a Safety service complying HSE instructions.* Insures execution of all planned and recommended measures.* Assists resolving immediate Safety & Maintenance concerns.* Support enhancing HSM operation according to the certified HSM plan,
IKEA standards and policies.
